---
const skills = [
  'JavaScript (ES6+)',
  'TypeScript',
  'React',
  'Java Spring Boot',
  'Node.js',
  'AWS',
];
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 fade-in-section">
  <h2 class="numbered-heading">About Me</h2>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
    <div class="text-base space-y-4" style="color: var(--slate);">
      <p>
        Hello! My name is Sayantan and I enjoy creating things that live on the internet.
        My interest in web development started back in 2020 when I decided to try building
        a custom theme — turns out hacking together buttons and HTML &amp; CSS taught me a lot!
      </p>
      <p>
        Fast-forward to today, and I've had the privilege of working at
        <span style="color: var(--green);">an innovative startup</span> and
        <span style="color: var(--green);">a large corporation</span>. My main focus these days
        is building accessible, inclusive products and digital experiences.
      </p>
      <p>Here are a few technologies I've been working with recently:</p>
      <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 mt-4 font-mono text-sm max-w-[400px]">
        {skills.map(skill => (
          <li class="flex items-center" style="color: var(--light-slate);">
            <span style="color: var(--green); margin-right: 8px;">▹</span>
            {skill}
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Profile image placeholder -->
    <div class="flex justify-center md:justify-start">
      <div class="relative w-[300px] h-[300px] group">
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-3 group-hover:translate-y-3"
          style="border: 2px solid var(--green); transform: translate(20px, 20px);"
        ></div>
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 rounded-lg z-10 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:bg-transparent"
          style="background: rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.1);"
        ></div>
        <div class="w-full h-full rounded-lg overflow-hidden relative z-0 group-hover:-translate-y-2 group-hover:-translate-x-2 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 opacity-80"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
